<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="en/getting-started/design-your-store/top-menu-and-footer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="120">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="en/getting-started/design-your-store/top-menu-and-footer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="122">The &quot;Recently viewed products&quot; menu item will only be displayed when the &quot;Recently viewed products&quot; page is enabled on the <strong sourcefile="en/getting-started/design-your-store/top-menu-and-footer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="122">Configuration → Settings → Catalog settings</strong> page (<em sourcefile="en/getting-started/design-your-store/top-menu-and-footer.md" sourcestartlinenumber="122">Additional sections</em> panel).</p>
